## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f5ef-189"><xref:System.Data.ParameterDirection>如果为`Output`, <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcParameter>并且与的执行不返回值, 则将包含 null 值。 <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcCommand></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f5ef-189">If the <xref:System.Data.ParameterDirection> is `Output`, and execution of the associated <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcCommand> does not return a value, the <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcParameter> will contain a null value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6f5ef-190">使用<xref:System.DBNull>类处理 Null 值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f5ef-190">Null values are handled using the <xref:System.DBNull> class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f5ef-191">`Output`在`InputOut`调用`ReturnValue` <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcCommand.ExecuteReader%2A> 或上的<xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcDataReader>时, 无法访问通过调用返回的、和参数。 `Dispose` <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcDataReader.Close%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f5ef-191">`Output`, `InputOut`, and `ReturnValue` parameters returned by calling <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcCommand.ExecuteReader%2A> cannot be accessed until you call <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcDataReader.Close%2A> or `Dispose` on the <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcDataReader>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f5ef-192">下面的示例创建<xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcParameter>并设置其一些属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f5ef-192">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.Odbc.OdbcParameter> and sets some of its properties.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Sub CreateMyProc(connection As OdbcConnection)  
  
   Dim command As OdbcCommand = connection.CreateCommand()  
   command.CommandText = "{ call MyProc(?,?,?) }"  
   command.Parameters.Add("", OdbcType.Int).Value = 1  
   command.Parameters.Add("", OdbcType.Decimal).Value = 2  
   command.Parameters.Add("", OdbcType.Decimal).Value = 3  
  
End Sub  
```  
  
```csharp  
public void CreateMyProc(OdbcConnection connection)   
{  
   OdbcCommand command = connection.CreateCommand();  
   command.CommandText = "{ call MyProc(?,?,?) }";  
   command.Parameters.Add("", OdbcType.Int).Value = 1;  
   command.Parameters.Add("", OdbcType.Decimal).Value = 2;  
   command.Parameters.Add("", OdbcType.Decimal).Value = 3;  
}  
```

  
  
